♪ When I hear
that trumpet sound ♪

47
00:05:18,777 --> 00:05:20,945
♪ I'm gonna rise
right out of the ground ♪

48
00:05:21,113 --> 00:05:23,531
♪ Ain't no grave ♪

49
00:05:23,699 --> 00:05:25,783
♪ Can hold my body down ♪

50
00:05:27,411 --> 00:05:31,288
♪ When I look
way down the river ♪

51
00:05:31,456 --> 00:05:33,916
♪ What do you think I see? ♪

52
00:05:34,084 --> 00:05:36,919
♪ I see me
a band of angels ♪

53
00:05:37,087 --> 00:05:39,463
♪ They're coming after me ♪

54
