♪ Well, look down yonder, Gabriel ♪

59
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:58,065
♪ Put your feet
on the land and sea ♪

60
00:05:58,233 --> 00:06:01,152
♪ But, Gabriel,
don't you blow your horn ♪

61
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:03,320
♪ Until you hear from me ♪

62
