♪ My name,
it is Sam Hall ♪

375
00:31:11,036 --> 00:31:13,746
♪ And I hate you,
one and all ♪

376
00:31:13,914 --> 00:31:16,082
♪ I hate you, one and all ♪

377
00:31:16,250 --> 00:31:18,668
♪ Damn your eyes ♪

378
00:31:20,420 --> 00:31:23,005
♪ To the gallows I must go,
I must go... ♪

379
00:31:23,173 --> 00:31:24,757
Get him!

380
00:31:24,925 --> 00:31:29,679
♪ To the gallows I must go,
I must go ♪

381
00:31:29,846 --> 00:31:32,682
♪ To the gallows I must go ♪

382
00:31:32,849 --> 00:31:35,434
♪ While you critters
down below ♪

383
00:31:35,602 --> 00:31:38,145
♪ Yell out,
"Sam, I told you so" ♪

384
00:31:38,313 --> 00:31:41,023
♪ Well, damn your eyes ♪

385
00:31:41,191 --> 00:31:43,901
♪ Now the preacher,
he did come ♪

386
00:31:44,069 --> 00:31:46,696
♪ He did come ♪

387
00:31:46,863 --> 00:31:49,115
♪ Now the preacher,
he did come ♪

388
00:31:49,283 --> 00:31:51,784
♪ He did come ♪

389
00:31:51,952 --> 00:31:54,245
Both:
♪ Now the preacher, he did come ♪

390
00:31:54,413 --> 00:31:56,747
♪ And he preached
till kingdom come... ♪

391
00:31:56,915 --> 00:31:59,333
James:
♪ Well, you can kiss my bloody bum ♪

392
00:31:59,501 --> 00:32:01,711
♪ Damn your eyes ♪

393
